OL,3,CFive pros to leave Strictly Come
OL,4,CDancing as full line-up confirmed
OL,6,FFive professional dancers have
OL,7,Fconfirmed they are leaving Strictly
OL,8,FCome Dancing as the BBC confirmed the
OL,9,Fline-up for the 2026 season.
OL,11,FThe BBC also confirmed new
OL,12,Fprofessionals would be recruited and
OL,13,Fannounced closer to the dancing show's
OL,14,Freturn in autumn to replace Gorka
OL,15,FMarquez, Michelle Tsiakkas, Karen
OL,16,FHauer, Nadiya Bychkova and Luba
OL,17,FMushtuk, who have left the show.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/8
