OL,3,CFive pros to leave Strictly Come
OL,4,CDancing as full line-up confirmed
OL,6,FReturning from 2025's series are
OL,7,FAlexis Warr, Amy Dowden, Aljaz
OL,8,FSkorjanec, Dianne Buswell, Johannes
OL,9,FRadebe, Jowita Przystal, Julian
OL,10,FCaillon, Kai Widdrington, Katya Jones,
OL,11,FLauren Oakley, Nancy Xu, Neil Jones,
OL,12,FNikita Kuzmin, Vito Coppola, and
OL,13,FCarlos Gu, who won last year's series
OL,14,Fwith former England footballer Karen
OL,15,FCarney.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/8
