OL,3,CFive pros to leave Strictly Come
OL,4,CDancing as full line-up confirmed
OL,6,FDowden returns after she was the first
OL,7,Fto leave last year's series, which saw
OL,8,Fher partnered with former The
OL,9,FApprentice candidate Tom Skinner, and
OL,10,Fwas forced to leave the 2024 series,
OL,11,Fwhere she was partnered with JB Gill,
OL,12,Fdue to injury, which led to her being
OL,13,Freplaced by Oakley.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/8
