OL,3,CFive pros to leave Strictly Come
OL,4,CDancing as full line-up confirmed
OL,6,FSkinner made headlines during his time
OL,7,Fon Strictly last year after he
OL,8,Fadmitted to cheating on his wife,
OL,9,FSinead just weeks after their wedding,
OL,10,Fin an interview with The Sun On
OL,11,FSunday, and went on to make
OL,12,Fallegations about the show including
OL,13,Fits voting system.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
