OL,3,CFive pros to leave Strictly Come
OL,4,CDancing as full line-up confirmed
OL,6,FThe judging panel of Craig Revel
OL,7,FHorwood, Motsi Mabuse, Anton Du Beke,
OL,8,Fand head judge Shirley Ballas have
OL,9,Falso all been announced as returning,
OL,10,Fwhile themed weeks including movies,
OL,11,Ficons, Halloween and musicals, plus
OL,12,Fthe Instant Dance challenge, which was
OL,13,Fintroduced last year, will also be
OL,14,Fback.
OL,16,FThere has been no news on who will
OL,17,Freplace Claudia Winkleman and Tess
OL,18,FDaly as hosts.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
