OL,3,CFive pros to leave Strictly Come
OL,4,CDancing as full line-up confirmed
OL,6,FThe BBC has also confirmed Strictly
OL,7,Fwill once again make its annual trip
OL,8,Fto Blackpool Tower Ballroom later this
OL,9,Fyear, and said further plans for the
OL,10,Fnew series would be announced in due
OL,11,Fcourse.
OL,13,FIt comes after Marquez announced last
OL,14,Fweek that he would be the latest
OL,15,Fprofessional dancer to depart the show
OL,16,Fafter 10 years performing on it.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
