OL,3,CFive pros to leave Strictly Come
OL,4,CDancing as full line-up confirmed
OL,6,FIn an Instagram post, the Spanish
OL,7,Fdancer said: "After last year's
OL,8,Fdecision to step down as a full-time
OL,9,Fprofessional due to scheduling
OL,10,Fconflicts between Strictly and Dancing
OL,11,FWith The Stars Spain, I've decided
OL,12,Fthat now is the time to hang up my
OL,13,Fdance shoes and say goodbye to
OL,14,FStrictly Come Dancing."
OL,16,FThe dancer's post was flooded with
OL,17,Ftributes from fans and stars alike,
OL,18,Fwith fellow departing dancers Hauer,
OL,19,FMushtuk and Bychkova offering their
OL,20,Fwell-wishes, each commenting with
OL,21,Fheart emojis.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
