OL,3,CFive pros to leave Strictly Come
OL,4,CDancing as full line-up confirmed
OL,6,FThe BBC has thanked each of the
OL,7,Fdeparting dancers for their time on
OL,8,Fthe show, praising Tsiakkas for her
OL,9,F"excellent performances" and
OL,10,F"professionalism", and Marquez for his
OL,11,F"exceptional contribution".
OL,13,FReporting History sees journalists
OL,14,Fjoin News At Ten anchor Tom Bradby to
OL,15,Frevisit their remarkable on-the-day
OL,16,Freports of the defining events of the
OL,17,Fmodern age. Listen to the episodes
OL,18,Fbelow...
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/8
